<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Acesso Restrito</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-2xl w-full bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <!-- Ícone de Cadeado -->
        <div class="mx-auto flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-red-100 mb-4">
          <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Acesso Restrito
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Você não possui permissão para acessar os recursos internos do site.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mb-6 text-left">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-yellow-800">
                Acesso Exclusivo para Membros
              </h3>
              <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-yellow-700">
                <p>
                  Para acessar os recursos internos, você precisa ter o cargo de 
                  <strong>"<%= @guild.required_discord_role_name || 'Membro' %>"</strong> 
                  no servidor Discord da guilda <strong><%= @guild.name %></strong>.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="text-left bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Como obter acesso:</h3>
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>Certifique-se de estar no servidor Discord da guilda</li>
              <li>Entre em contato com um administrador do servidor</li>
              <li>Solicite o cargo necessário para acesso ao site</li>
              <li>Após receber o cargo, faça logout e login novamente</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center mt-6">
            <%= button_to "Fazer Logout", logout_path, 
                          method: :delete,
                          class: "px-6 py-3 bg-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition duration-200" %>
            
            <% if @guild.discord_guild_id.present? %>
              <a href="https://discord.com/channels/<%= @guild.discord_guild_id %>" 
                 target="_blank"
                 class="px-6 py-3 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition duration-200 text-center">
                Ir para o Discord
              </a>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
            Você está logado como <strong><%= current_user.discord_username %></strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
